These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, kale, pepper, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, ferret, frog
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating radish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the owner of the bird is not the person eating radish##6
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
 8. the person eating kale is not the owner of the frog##6
 9. the person eating apple is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person eating kale is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
12. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
13. the person eating radish is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | apple         | radish     | pepper     | kale         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Pet   | bird       | guinea-pig | frog | ferret       |

