.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
House: wooden, craftsman, modern, townhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, documentary, horror
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, colombian, dutch
 1. the modern house is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
 2. the person watching horror movies is not the brazilian##6
 3. the colombian is somewhere between the craftsman house and the person watching horror movies##7
 4. the brazilian is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 6. the colombian is the person watching action movies##1
 7. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the dutch is between the wooden house and the colombian##2
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the wooden house##8
10. the modern house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
11. the american is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| House          | craftsman      | modern      | townhouse | wooden |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action    | horror | crime     |
| Nationality   | american    | colombian | dutch  | brazilian |

