 6. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the fan of trance##8
11. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

