 1. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person traveling to hannover##6
 4. the person traveling to miami is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 7. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
10. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
11. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
12. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person traveling to paris##6

.:: Answer ::.
